# Enterprise ERP System

An offline-first, enterprise-grade ERP platform built with **Kotlin**, **Jetpack Compose**, **Room SQLite Database**, **Material Design 3**, and **Google Gemini AI**.

Designed for modern enterprises requiring secure business operations, double-entry accounting, inventory management, manufacturing execution, HR administration, document control, workflow automation, compliance auditing, and AI-powered decision support.

