# 🛡️ Why This Application Differs From Typical ERP Apps

## 1. Zero Dummy Affordances

### Typical Applications

* Mocked Data
* Fake Success Messages
* Temporary State

### Enterprise ERP

* Real Room SQLite Database
* Persistent Data Storage
* Live Transaction Processing
* Queryable Business Records

Every inventory transaction, accounting entry, approval action, and HR operation is written directly to the database.

---

## 2. Active Contrast Alignment

### Typical Applications

* Dense Interfaces
* Poor Visibility
* Operator Fatigue

### Enterprise ERP

* Material 3 Slate Palette
* Optimized Contrast
* High-Speed Visual Scanning
* Operational Status Highlighting

---

## 3. Dynamic Canvas Rendering

### Typical Applications

* Static Images
* Fixed Layouts

### Enterprise ERP

* Adaptive Jetpack Compose Canvas
* Dynamic Barcode Generation
* Theme-Aware Rendering
* Scalable Vector Graphics

---

## 4. Compliance Audit Architecture

### Typical Applications

Only display current data.

### Enterprise ERP

Every modification automatically creates a historical compliance record showing:

* Who changed data
* What changed
* Previous value
* Updated value
* When it changed

---

## 5. Verification-Gated Accounting

Unlike ordinary mobile finance apps:

* Double-entry accounting validation
* Balance enforcement
* Real-time financial integrity checks
* Enterprise compliance standards

---

## 6. Manufacturing QA Gatekeeping

Products cannot move into finished inventory until quality inspection has been successfully completed.

