## ⚙️ Installation

### Prerequisites

* Android Studio Hedgehog or newer
* Android SDK 34+
* JDK 17+
* Google Gemini API Key (Optional)

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/enterprise-erp-system.git
```

### Build Project

```bash
./gradlew build
```

### Run Application

```bash
./gradlew installDebug
```

